{"tid":1667673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"三十幾歲A0, 好容易就對女仔有興趣…","createTime":"2019-10-21T14:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T14:23:57.000Z","uid":122231,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"902f81a59881df9a28810b3c78ce6c341540a3c9","tid":1667673,"uid":122231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"好似興趣班同班有一兩個睇落ok嘅<br />\n好想識吓佢哋<br />\n<br />\n但冷靜D照下鏡<br />\n睇下自己個樣(肥矮毒)<br />\n同埋睇下本銀行存摺有幾多錢(冇錢)<br />\n就覺得自卑<br />\n覺得如果去識佢哋<br />\n俾佢哋覺得唔係純粹識朋友而係別有用心<br />\n<br />\n之前舊公司走嗰陣又係咁<br />\n問咗個女同事contact<br />\n結果add都唔敢add就咁冇咗<br />\n<br />\n係咪肥毒撚咁就一世?<br />\n我知㗎，一直有做運動，食又盡量控制<br />\n但半年只係減得十幾磅<br />\n錢我又比同年齡嘅人搵得少儲得少<br />\n<br />\n我其實真係好廢，但我實在冇條件去大膽d<br />\n一件一定失敗嘅事，做咗咪只會更傷心?<br />\n似乎我點叫春都係一世A0㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n講完算啦，反正我係無能用"},{"pid":"dedbd1f7e81820bd09aff4967e85a29837bcb623","tid":1667673,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"叫雞"},{"pid":"4ff4cc7818cb044eeff7fbf66cd5e1ccfbfe5f30","tid":1667673,"uid":179975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27670aa034b363e1fedd235f30e63c91f2cec404","tid":1667673,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"拎張相出黎 大家比下意見"},{"pid":"071ae72989b14576a19305cb89ce50d4dfcfd895","tid":1667673,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27670aa034b363e1fedd235f30e63c91f2cec404","tid":1667673,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"拎張相出黎 大家比下意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"601d1536eb26810d2b3e900bec8fd86bdd085e0b","tid":1667673,"uid":208285,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"半年十幾磅唔錯啦"},{"pid":"915403e81a7829612e7ec8a098929386b9dcf439","tid":1667673,"uid":5553